HEADWORD: Juneberry
<hw>June"ber`ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>The small applelike berry of American trees of genus
<gen>Amelanchier</gen>; -- also called <altname>service
berry</altname>.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The shrub or tree which bears
this fruit; -- also called <altname>shad bush</altname>, and
<altname>shad tree</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

